Sports Direct Names Charlie McCreevy Non-Executive Director

-- B y   D a v i d   A l t a n e r
-- 
2011-04-01T08:01:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-01/sports-direct-names-charlie-mccreevy-non-executive-director-1-.html
Sports Direct International Plc (SPD) 
appointed Charlie McCreevy, a former European Union commissioner
and Irish minister, as a non-executive director.  McCreevy, who is currently a non-executive director at
 Ryanair Holdings Plc (RYA) , was formerly EU commissioner for internal
markets and services.  He was also minister for finance, tourism and social
welfare in several Irish governments, the Mansfield, England-
based company said today in a statement distributed by the
Regulatory News Service.  To contact the reporter on this story:
David Altaner in London at 
 daltaner@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net  